<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_FILL_MODE">
    <summary>
      <para>Specifies the fill mode to use when rendering triangles.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>Fill mode is specified in a <see cref="D3D12_RASTERIZER_DESC" /> structure.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/cd3dx12-rasterizer-desc">CD3DX12_RASTERIZER_DESC</seealso>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-enumerations">Core Enumerations</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_FILL_MODE.D3D12_FILL_MODE_WIREFRAME">
    <summary>
      <para>Draw lines connecting the vertices. Adjacent vertices are not drawn.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_FILL_MODE.D3D12_FILL_MODE_SOLID">
    <summary>
      <para>Fill the triangles formed by the vertices. Adjacent vertices are not drawn.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>